snippet.title: The AFC Podcast
snippet.description:
This platform is for us to have open and candid conversations about stories in the news.
I get so many emails and message from people that love what I do, and I wanna continue bringing great content to Youtube! I want to thank you in advance for your consideration in contributing to my platform!
